text: Wasserlosen is a municipality in Schweinfurt, Bavaria, Germany. The villages in this municipality are: *Brebersdorf *Burghausen bei Schweinfurt *Greßthal *Kaisten *Rütschenhausen *Schwemmelsbach *Wasserlosen *Wülfershausen ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Schweinfurt (district)
